metadata.description:
Minato Chan remains the final human link to the Yokai realm, and her presence is critical to the foundation of the Tanukiland. She embraces the building spirit of those on the path of shape-shifting.

Minato Chan is the protagonist of Tanukiverse. She embarks on a journey where she learns about the rich history of Tanuki through a variety of exciting experiences. 

What shall unfold, remains a secret...
  

Note: This Minato Chan was created from Candy #740 from Minato Chitoseame Candy collection :  https://opensea.io/collection/minato-chitoseame-candies
